{
  "stem": "12564.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't last a half an hour, and Ben Gurion and Dayan came in, flew in, in the first line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were sitting and asking what happened, to find out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know what all this, it was, what they give after this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The planes start bombing for three days with-- [? at a roar ?] on their fortress.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the end of the third day, we set up-- yeah, what they call it-- lines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every 50 feet, another line of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they picked, in the first line, the best units.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We found out that the Arabs in the fortress have no water anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were-- and one day, they run out with the bayonets on us too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they came out in the thousands from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were working very good with the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And finally, we took to them alive, more than 1,100, after the-- after the several hours fighting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we inspected their bunkers, to our dismay, none of them were damaged from all the bombing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "None of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You could drive a jeep in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- they made one mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The water when they pulled, is from a place where Moses hit the stone and got water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They call it in Arabic and Hebrew, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Al-Qassim. ?] It's 50 kilometers away from the fortress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Our parachute jumped over there and cut off the water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this made them give up or final fight-- they would try to go out of this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And at that time, I didn't know when we reached, already, the [? sewer ?] canal after this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was-- you know, it took us 17 hours to reach the [? sewer ?] canal.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
